msgctxt "72_Kamei"
msgid "Unh... That was... amazing..."
msgstr "Unh... Eso fue... asombroso..."

msgctxt "84_Tanimura"
msgid "Why'd you have to make it so difficult?"
msgstr "¿Por qué tuviste que hacerlo tan difícil?"

msgctxt "108_Tanimura"
msgid "(Hey, I think that's Kamei.)"
msgstr "(Oye, creo que es Kamei)."

msgctxt "120_Tanimura"
msgid "Kamei!"
msgstr "¡Kamei!"

msgctxt "132_Kamei"
msgid "What? Who are you? How do you know me?"
msgstr "¿Qué? ¿Quién eres? ¿Cómo me conoces?"

msgctxt "144_Tanimura"
msgid "I'm from the Dragon Palace. It's time to pay your tab."
msgstr "Soy del Palacio del Dragón. Es hora de pagar la cuenta."

msgctxt "156_Kamei"
msgid "Hmph. I had to beat down that old man just the other day.\\r\n"\n"I guess they'll never learn."
msgstr "Hmph. Tuve que golpear a ese viejo el otro día.\\r\n"\n"Supongo que nunca aprenderán."

msgctxt "168_Kamei"
msgid "They don't call me \"Doctor Badass\" for nothing, you know.\\r\n"\n"I guess you'll soon find out!"
msgstr "No me llaman \"Doctor Brutal\" por nada, ya sabes.\\r\n"\n"¡Supongo que pronto lo descubrirás!"

